lemma PCF_lr_POR_delta: "PCF_lr (unlr POR.delta)"
(*<*)
  using logical_relation_POR PCF_consts_rel_POR by fastforce
(*>*)
text\<open>

This is the truth-table for POR rendered as a vector: we seek a
